# Upstream-deleted agent files; install.sh --update prunes them from the
# agent install dir. Paths are relative to the agent INSTALL_DIR (i.e. to
# agent/ in the repo). When an agent runtime file is deleted upstream, add it
# here AND (with the agent/ prefix) to tools/installer/removed-paths.manifest,
# which cleans the manager-host deploy mirror that feeds the agent tarball.
# Format: file|<PR>|<install-relative path>
